title: Green Market Natural Foods
description:
Small, well-stocked natural food store. They offer a wide 
selection of natural and gourmet foods, vitamins, herbs, 
and nutritional supplements, as well as natural pet 
food, natural body care, and organic and local produce. 
They also carry many special diet items like gluten-free, 
vegan, and more. Cafe serves an assortment of fresh 
salads, sandwiches, smoothies, and natural frozen yogurt.
